23 SECTION 1. Arkansas Code § 20-77-147(b), concerning reimbursement for
24 diagnostic laboratory services is amended to read as follows:
25 (b) The program shall set the annual cap for:
26 (1) Diagnostic laboratory services, not including radiology
27 services, of at least:
28 (A) Five five hundred dollars ($500); or
29 (B) One thousand eight hundred dollars ($1,800) if the
30 beneficiary is diagnosed with chronic pain or is being treated for pain
31 management; and
32 (2) Radiology services of at least five hundred dollars ($500).
